high_descs: turn left and walk over to the garbage bin at the end of the room up ahead on the right
grab the CD out of the garbage bin
turn right and walk over to the desk there, but then turn right again and walk forwards just a few steps
place the CD inside of the pullout drawer which is on the right side of the desk
turn around and walk to the wall up ahead, then turn right to face the desk again
grab the CD off of the desk there
turn right to walk forwards a few steps again
place the CD inside of the same drawer on the right side of the desk that you put the other CD in

high_descs: Turn right and go across the room to the trash can.

Put the CD in the top drawer of the nightstand.

Pick up the CD on the desk.

Put the CD in the top drawer of the nightstand.

high_descs: Turn left and walk over to the small green bin against the wall.
Pick up the disc out of the green bin.
Turn right and walk over to the wooden desk, then turn right and walk forward.
Open the upper drawer of the nightstand next to the bed and put the disc inside, then close the drawer.
Turn around and walk forward, then turn right and walk up to the wooden desk.
Pick up the disc off of the wooden desk.
Turn around and walk towards the door, then turn left and walk forward.
